.row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;

    .col-md-4 {
        flex: 1 0 calc(33.333% - 20px); // Adjust the width as needed
    }
}
// The "display: flex" property is added to the .product-card class to arrange the content inside each card vertically.
// Flex properties are used to control the spacing and alignment of elements within each card.
// For the product card grid, Flexbox is applied to the .row class, which allows for a responsive and centered display of product cards.
